race.comment: JUNGLE JOHNNY (2) shapes well after a sharp run last time, finishing third in a NG at this track in 29.51. In form and rates on top this time. ALLAN KEEPING (6) was game in defeat when finished in the minors last start over the 400m at Bulli, running a quick 22.26 in a Grade 4/5. Fast run latest and rates a key player again. FALSE WITNESS (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 5.5 lengths sixth (29.92) but scored four back at The Gardens (29.31). Has a good record here at this journey. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Likely to play a prominent role.  Something for the Multiples: GETS LATE EARLY (4)
